ht|d|va|8|CS||FP||CP||AT|^B@2^Y@3You can summarize the Monty Hall's TV show to the following three scenarios if you pick curtain ##1 for example.
## 1: The prize is behind curtain 3. The only curtain that Monty Hall can open with small prize behind it is 
^ccurtain 2--his choice is RESTRICTED to curtain 2. Contestant must switch.
## 2: The prize is behind curtain 2. The only curtain that Monty Hall can open with small prize behind it is 
^ccurtain 3--his choice is RESTRICTED to curtain 3. Contestant must switch.
## 3: The prize is behind curtain 1. Monty Hall can open either curtain 2 or 3--his choice is not restricted 
^cand the contestant loses. |
